    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Zest the<strong> lemon</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Roll the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-copy-4-1688139500930-x200.jpg",
