            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a small pot over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, add 4 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [8 tbsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong> with the <strong>lemon zest</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, the juice of 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1] </span><strong>lemon</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook until the butter has melted – this is your <strong>lemon & garlic butter sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
